  <brief_title>Effect of Chrysanthemum Flower Oil and Its Dose-dependency on Hyperuricemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Parallel Group Study to Evaluate the Effect of Chrysanthemum Flower Oil and Its Dose-dependency in Subjects With Hyperuricemia</official_title>
